<item>
            <title>[LU-18691] quota interop w/64k pages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18691</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In vvp_io_write_commit() if EDQUOT is hit 64k interop logic needs to be checked to determine if the I/O will hang.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the server supports unaligned DIO the same interop logic can be used from LUS-12175 / &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17525&quot; title=&quot;Unaligned DIO interop with different page sizes fails&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17525&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17525&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and this check can be skipped and the I/O may succeed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
